{"tid":1095192,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"[有圖] DIY 陶瓷介指一隻","createTime":"2019-04-06T23:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T04:50:21.000Z","uid":168808,"like":1332,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"d949d7b11809d9b83dea5eb6418d3eaedb0dec4a","tid":1095192,"uid":168808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T23:34:53.000Z","msg":"大家平時見到嘅青花瓷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pNaCekg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpNaCekg.png&h=4aacb4fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係用一種叫porcelain嘅clay去整出黎(係由瓷石、高岭土組成)<br />\n小妹好鍾意Diy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我就用同樣嘅物料去整左隻魔腦bb介指 <br />\n最後揀左哩隻-&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當你搓好個初形等佢乾，就可以放入窑。<br />\n經過第一次素燒係800幾度，燒嘅原因係等佢變硬、收縮，唔會同d 釉(顔色)溝埋一pat<br />\n上埋色係咁嘅撚樣:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kn6azm1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKn6azm1.png&h=bdd95c69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後再燒佢1260-1280度<br />\n咁就完全啦！<br />\n完成品: <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TDwNBEg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTDwNBEg.png&h=6b386198&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樓主上手圖:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B72MScN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB72MScN.png&h=1ceac86b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實陶瓷好有趣，亦有好多可能性，唔一定係整杯杯碟碟，正正因為一跌就碎，顯得更矜貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而我今次用嘅綠色有種半透明嘅感覺，似玉，加上美女手製，20年後等我出左名，哩嚿似垃圾嘅野將會價值不菲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254f3039fdedbd37e6c70ae5c27ed3f565b95de4","tid":1095192,"uid":41423,"like":96,"dislike":0,"score":96,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T23:39:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba011512c69ed0b81e20e4ba605c3cdb1bac366","tid":1095192,"uid":41423,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T23:39:38.000Z","msg":"樓豬係邊上course<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"897bccfefe73a9c77200218d52da357c8484db11","tid":1095192,"uid":1348,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T23:40:07.000Z","msg":"樓主上個post 都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c4244a5bf8933d2310c70f18205c2070cf40d2","tid":1095192,"uid":1348,"like":69,"dislike":3,"score":66,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T23:40:58.000Z","msg":"用黎求婚一流"},{"pid":"b729fa96ee909ddb85f93bec2a529c52d018d121","tid":1095192,"uid":3063,"like":86,"dislike":0,"score":86,"quote":{"pid":"a0c4244a5bf8933d2310c70f18205c2070cf40d2","tid":1095192,"uid":1348,"like":69,"dislike":3,"score":66,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T23:40:58.000Z","msg":"用黎求婚一流"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T23:46:04.000Z","msg":"身痕？"},{"pid":"914e6e6d5416b5f7d9ac98880014f8d6d9cc96b9","tid":1095192,"uid":168808,"like":130,"dislike":1,"score":129,"quote":{"pid":"7ba011512c69ed0b81e20e4ba605c3cdb1bac366","tid":1095192,"uid":41423,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T23:39:38.000Z","msg":"樓豬係邊上course<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T23:52:57.000Z","msg":"我係大學修哩科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （等乞米）<br />\n但如果出去學好貴，一堂都300-800<br />\n但你買成包porcelain clay 都係150/10kg<br />\n10kg可以用到好耐 而d釉每隻色190 我整隻介指只係用左幾滴 而拎去燒一次好似都係30蚊 <br />\n<br />\n如果想整個件作品係會用到好多不同顔色先去上course，會慳好多錢"},{"pid":"c10661a585208de50a1a32cd762688426798d09f","tid":1095192,"uid":168808,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"897bccfefe73a9c77200218d52da357c8484db11","tid":1095192,"uid":1348,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T23:40:07.000Z","msg":"樓主上個post 都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T23:55:07.000Z","msg":"你有留意<img src=\"/a