umbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB72MScN.png&h=1ceac86b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實陶瓷好有趣，亦有好多可能性，唔一定係整杯杯碟碟，正正因為一跌就碎，顯得更矜貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而我今次用嘅綠色有種半透明嘅感覺，似玉，加上美女手製，20年後等我出左名，哩嚿似垃圾嘅野將會價值不菲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T06:44:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">戒指</span>"},{"pid":"2a0f1d53527d6545dadd7c30cc73b63449b767d7","tid":1095192,"uid":68363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d03487207a1c8e20f114013cbf315618eafa1321","tid":1095192,"uid":1348,"like":27,"dislike":3,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"914e6e6d5416b5f7d9ac98880014f8d6d9cc96b9","tid":1095192,"uid":168808,"like":130,"dislike":1,"score":129,"quote":{"pid":"7ba011512c69ed0b81e20e4ba605c3cdb1bac366","tid":1095192,"uid":41423,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T23:39:38.000Z","msg":"樓豬係邊上course<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T23:52:57.000Z","msg":"我係大學修哩科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （等乞米）<br />\n但如果出去學好貴，一堂都300-800<br />\n但你買成包porcelain clay 都係150/10kg<br />\n10kg可以用到好耐 而d釉每隻色190 我整隻介指只係用左幾滴 而拎去燒一次好似都係30蚊 <br />\n<br />\n如果想整個件作品係會用到好多不同顔色先去上course，會慳好多錢"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T02:00:57.000Z","msg":"我去火炭工廈整好似2-300<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9FYHruU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9FYHruU.png&h=a8dcffee&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T06:45:07.000Z","msg":"幾靚喎"},{"pid":"8c71b71f4e8ac7f264af7528b07b60ec309441cc","tid":1095192,"uid":3722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T09:29:07.000Z","msg":"樓主讀BU? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a8a9b08b8c21994af94ef4eff182c644f0d97a8","tid":1095192,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T09:32: